  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/f631dcec0d66bf1b6c557415b144e5b5.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a member of the exploration and investigation team. Your job is to collect enough evidence about the monster that has attacked the station.  Venture across derelict stations and planets. Find a way to survive monster's attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/efd2b0248135e7b8ad38ee26f5350216.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember that biomorphs can corrupt one of your team members into working on their side! Beware betrayal! As a corrupted player you are on the quest to disrupt and trick other players into thinking that it's another type of a monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/2cff1b6dca5378c798c3ae6416a667e6.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/2cff1b6dca5378c798c3ae6416a667e6.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/2cff1b6dca5378c798c3ae6416a667e6.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other players can vote against suspicious player. Enough votes will result in quick and painless death. <br>Keep your friends close, but enemies even closer!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/20a4155f5c9d3a3ef70ca10b5110572c.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/20a4155f5c9d3a3ef70ca10b5110572c.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/20a4155f5c9d3a3ef70ca10b5110572c.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/2ed1525a9cf46c32c19415034cd0696a.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Identify more than 20 monster types with unique traits and personalities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/ee7ec168e74af8a242cc377863d1be82.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/ee7ec168e74af8a242cc377863d1be82.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/ee7ec168e74af8a242cc377863d1be82.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 5 maps available for exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/664edbd5ad2e826b1f36edc2ef83fe9c.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/664edbd5ad2e826b1f36edc2ef83fe9c.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/664edbd5ad2e826b1f36edc2ef83fe9c.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience immersion with realistic graphics, high interactivity and fine tuned sounds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/598b3ec82e0466552e8481b0b0582d43.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/598b3ec82e0466552e8481b0b0582d43.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/598b3ec82e0466552e8481b0b0582d43.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your voice is recognized and understood by the monster and can even be stolen and used against your team!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 difficulties including custom one to tailor your own experience.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space is Deep and Dark place to go alone. So, bring friends, or join open lobbies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/329392902bff2a567a98b7bc1d4d667e.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/329392902bff2a567a98b7bc1d4d667e.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/329392902bff2a567a98b7bc1d4d667e.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/f631dcec0d66bf1b6c557415b144e5b5.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a member of the exploration and investigation team. Your job is to collect enough evidence about the monster that has attacked the station.  Venture across derelict stations and planets. Find a way to survive monster's attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.webm?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/796a02d3abd3ddb43f1852114e49ec36.mp4?t=1744967921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/efd2b0248135e7b8ad38ee26f5350216.avif?t=1744967921\" width=800 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember that biomorphs can corrupt one of your team members into working on their side! Beware betrayal! As a corrupted player you are on the quest to disrupt and trick other players into thinking that it's another type of a monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/2cff1b6dca5378c798c3ae6416a667e6.poster.avif?t=1744967921\" width